name: Web Template
tagline: Basic Template & Boiler code for html website.
body:
### Welcome to WebTemplate

This is a basic webtemplate for html css javascript. it hopefully will save you some time, and remove the need for you to remember the basic starting code.

I have also included normalize.css, this sources from: http://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/ all credits going to necolas.

This was last updated 21 Feb 14
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
